{"tid":2191554,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"唔好再鬥黃, 黃絲只係志同道合既人, 從來無規定要係操行分A+ 先可以叫同路人","createTime":"2020-09-06T13:45:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T05:28:53.000Z","uid":334720,"like":140,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"545d455f2852a2ae528f2e96cb45df154b613b1e","tid":2191554,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T13:45:33.000Z","msg":"首先黃色經濟圈 / 黃店門檻係:<br />\n會屌警暴 屌政府管治問題, 追求民主既, 我就敢幫襯<br />\n<br />\n黃絲都係一樣<br />\n你估出黎遊行既人, 個個要操行分拎A+ / 道德100分既人? <br />\n會出黎遊行既, 肯定有:<br />\nMK 厹<br />\n傳銷<br />\n騙子<br />\n吸毒<br />\n...<br />\n...<br />\n唔同背景既人<br />\n<br />\n咁係咪就代表人地唔係黃? <br />\n理撚得人地本身係乜野 有咩好嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 洗唔洗考牌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n莫問出處啦唔該<br />\n<br />\n咁得閒8掛人地內鬥 嘈交, 仲周圍share<br />\n不如幫下手屌下藍絲 同做FB TWITTER IG 鍵盤戰士啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee62b9a9b0583f5127a5be50e3d647e3904b69b7","tid":2191554,"uid":98473,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T13:47:00.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 一個人做左錯事<br />\n比人批評有乜問題<br />\n點解係要冠上黃絲依個名？"},{"pid":"e9018b4cbd5aef55ed049de9a7b1a8632ce00840","tid":2191554,"uid":245849,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ee62b9a9b0583f5127a5be50e3d647e3904b69b7","tid":2191554,"uid":98473,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T13:47:00.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 一個人做左錯事<br />\n比人批評有乜問題<br />\n點解係要冠上黃絲依個名？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T13:48:28.000Z","msg":"結果咪得乖乖仔同聖人同共產黨鬥，之後好似張學良咁俾共產黨呃囉"},{"pid":"a3269b3d60b945568db2326ba0ea41adebc5e1bd","tid":2191554,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T13:48:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"31dcf8e43ab7eb38411c4c7fe21b59c712a94f02","tid":2191554,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T13:49:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2cfc39d1e6969ad3a5b019231853180ed516d56","tid":2191554,"uid":52949,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T13:50:00.000Z","msg":"其實好耐之前已經覺得鬥黃呢件事好唔掂<br />\n<br />\n只要大家方向一致就ok..又要屌黎屌去<br />\n連龍門做咁多野都可以比自己友話<br />\n<br />\n唔心淡都假啦"},{"pid":"5276826ebc570d99f54607f94bf3458cfeede8ee","tid":2191554,"uid":334720,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ee62b9a9b0583f5127a5be50e3d647e3904b69b7","tid":2191554,"uid":98473,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T13:47:00.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 一個人做左錯事<br />\n比人批評有乜問題<br />\n點解係要冠上黃絲依個名？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T14:19:58.000Z","msg":"上面提到黃絲既問題<br />\n其實藍絲都一樣有<br />\n唔去嘈藍絲先, 走去嘈黃絲先, 為D乜<br />\n<br />\n又要想黃圈好, 又要公審又要嘈通天<br />\n最好笑既係, D咩內鬥 嘈交個D, 其實本身就唔多人知既<br />\n亦都無乜人care<br />\n但下下比連登仔擺哂上黎 搞到愈黎愈嚴重<br />\n大把野可以嘈, 係要嘈左自己人先搞咩鬼<br />\n<br />\n搞清楚而家我地係應該對人唔對事 (黃VS藍) <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad8c03eb81d9761232fdabc6db47d86b3a9af2fa","tid":2191554,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:43:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7816de195eab2cb6cedcebe9b354eae156a1e09","tid":2191554,"uid":22341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:44:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4862a7fb21ea65678f9bc256c8fec37865a8cbea","tid":2191554,"uid":59976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:46:50.000Z","msg":"講得岩，黃絲小小野就即刻批鬥分化，連人地藍絲既團結強大一成都學唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a135cc4577aacff4e75e51cf0f56768102cb5a","tid":2191554,"uid":92448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:51:07.000Z","msg":"殺人犯都可以黃, 10優都可以藍<br />\n黃藍基本上係睇個信念, 同埋有冇人性"},{"pid":"f494d64ef0709d9763030de04e4a5058d2e6e3da","tid":2191554,"uid":334720,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"4862a7fb21ea65678f9bc256c8fec37865a8cbea","tid":2191554,"uid":59976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:46:50.000Z","msg":"講得岩，黃絲小小野就即刻批鬥分化，連人地藍絲既團結強大一成都學唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:51:18.000Z","msg":"例子:<br />\n大家成日笑9 DAVID, 話佢attention seeker 又柒開<br />\n但有無見過藍絲走去笑9大波MAN <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ed264e370fd4b0dffc2770795912e332a28f42b","tid":2191554,"uid":219244,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:52:39.000Z","msg":"咪係<br />\n藍絲最鐘意睇我地互屌<br />\n如果互屌就可以贏嘅話我每日都屌係老母<br />\n真係唔明點解黃絲咁鐘意互相批鬥<br />\n好下學下政府、藍絲死攬黑警啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>1<span class=\"x-large\"> 講晦氣說話冇用</span><br />\n<br />\n講晦氣說話絕對唔係出路<br />\n如果講完有用嘅話我講1000次都得</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><strong><em>2 <span class=\"xx-large\">幸災樂禍嘅一定唔係手足</span></em></strong><br />\n呢啲賤人大家見到可以見一個block一個，唔需要幫佢推post<br />\n<br />\n無論係行街被圍捕、定係勇武被便衣當場斷正<br />\n真同路人應該見到手足被捕只會心痛<br />\n<span class=\"large\">絕對唔會<span class=\"x-large\">落井</span><span class=\"xx-large\">下石</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"violet\"><strong><em>3 我知大家心情唔好 但都<span class=\"x-large\">請你唔好冷嘲熱諷</span></em><br />\n你講一句，人地學10句，好快就散Band<br />\n大家好聲好氣先可以理性討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e1699cc7dc35661003e59e095216818aee9adbe1","tid":2191554,"uid":219244,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f2cfc39d1e6969ad3a5b019231853180ed516d56","tid":219155