.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只要係黃 偷呃 拐騙既都唔屌得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6370e81a713cfabca7bd35ff8e21994e4644b19e","tid":2191554,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19f40cc81b9df98ec5958c6cb54a259f40e85553","tid":2191554,"uid":278219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:57:44.000Z","msg":"都on9既，黃藍係政見 ，唔係做錯事既擋箭牌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T16:13:02.000Z","msg":"咁人地做錯事又關你鬼事咩，黃圈幾時要政治潔癖到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"853544a045b9ab2fdfc772643566cf8fba3760a7","tid":2191554,"uid":278219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6370e81a713cfabca7bd35ff8e21994e4644b19e","tid":2191554,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19f40cc81b9df98ec5958c6cb54a259f40e85553","tid":2191554,"uid":278219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:57:44.000Z","msg":"都on9既，黃藍係政見 ，唔係做錯事既擋箭牌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T16:13:02.000Z","msg":"咁人地做錯事又關你鬼事咩，黃圈幾時要政治潔癖到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T16:23:32.000Z","msg":"你都on9 討論區大把都唔關自己事咩都唔可以講？<br />\n黃店服務差都會屌9 ，都要係消費者角度屌佢<br />\n唔洗要100分，但唔會縱容劣質服務個d"},{"pid":"6e8fd350f6e486a0785d13378ffc6580cbf69c5c","tid":2191554,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T16:24:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed31688ea893640308100f2d232012290d8b221b","tid":2191554,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2540b689feeffa1192d8e0b0d4717b8432eb66d0","tid":2191554,"uid":57797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T16:10:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只要係黃 偷呃 拐騙既都唔屌得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T16:51:51.000Z","msg":"ching你D邏輯都好唔掂<br />\n無人叫你唔好屌<br />\n但大把野可以屌 其實可以分一分次序<br />\n一邊屌9藍絲 政府<br />\n同時間又內鬥<br />\n識分身咩<br />\nfocus少少, 團結少少<br />\n樣樣都屌 只會搞到自己好似D支那人咁款, <br />\n覺得自己識得指出問題好叻, 肅清社會不是, 立下大功<br />\n但其實做完呢D野係完全無助於呢場運動"},{"pid":"e7b6f8db06be56de710a0cedcb245f14ae41035f","tid":2191554,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T16:56:07.000Z","msg":"黃=支持香港民主,爭取香港公義,的確唔=操行A+,如果有1個自私男人,但佢係好爸爸,想仔女將來生活係有保障嘅香港,佢都可以係黃"},{"pid":"8c1c561eac87f2292da9483b6e9361d301d97c09","tid":2191554,"uid":128991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T17:00:42.000Z","msg":"其實香港人作為較弱一方要贏，一定係要搵出最大公因數&hellip;&hellip;齋講道德而唔講策略，根本冇得贏"},{"pid":"c99c6d928eb2ffeda2913efc584107b40ad4fc4f","tid":2191554,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T17:03:00.000Z","msg":"屌黑警唔屌政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"f494d64ef0709d9763030de04e4a5058d2e6e3da","tid":2191554,"uid":334720,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:51:18.000Z","msg":"例子:<br />\n大家成日笑9 DAVID, 話佢attention seeker 又柒開<br />\n但有無見過藍絲走去笑9大波MAN <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}